| Code | Error Class | Category | Retryable |
|------|------------|----------|-----------|
| `CIRCULAR_DEPENDENCY` | CircularDependencyError | permanent | false |
| `MISSING_DEPENDENCY` | MissingDependencyError | permanent | false |
